{"word":"κατέχω","slug":"κατέχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰατέχω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔχω\">ἔχω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘prevent action’, <b>hold back, restrain <a href='B:490 4:42'>Lk 4:42</a>; <a href='B:600 2:6'>2 Th 2:6f</a>; suppress <a href='B:520 1:18'>Ro 1:18</a>; control <a href='B:500 5:4'>J 5:4</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:520 7:6'>Ro 7:6</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘maintain a strong interest in or right to’ <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> hold fast <a href='B:490 8:15'>Lk 8:15</a>; <a href='B:530 11:2'>1 Cor 11:2</a></b> (maintain); <b><a href='B:530 15:2'>15:2</a>; <a href='B:590 5:21'>1 Th 5:21</a>; <a href='B:640 1:1'>Phlm 13</a></b> (retain, keep); <b><a href='B:650 3:6'>Hb 3:6</a>, <a href='B:650 3:14'>14</a>; <a href='B:650 10:23'>10:23</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> possess, own <a href='B:530 7:30'>1 Cor 7:30</a>; <a href='B:540 6:10'>2 Cor 6:10</a>.</b> In <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense, <b>occupy <a href='B:490 14:9'>Lk 14:9</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp> head for,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> nautical <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ t.t.\">t.t.</a> <b><a href='B:510 27:40'>Ac 27:40</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κατέχεεν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κατήγαγον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}